@startuml
title Devils Resting - Backend Architecture
top to bottom direction
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam backgroundColor #ffffff
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center
skinparam wrapWidth 220
skinparam nodesep 45
skinparam ranksep 55
skinparam roundcorner 10
skinparam ArrowColor #687385
skinparam ArrowThickness 1.1
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam rectangle {
  BorderColor #c8d0db
  BackgroundColor #f7f9fc
  FontColor #1f2937
}
skinparam package {
  BorderColor #c8d0db
  BackgroundColor #f7f9fc
  FontColor #1f2937
}
skinparam component {
  BorderColor #9fb0c7
  BackgroundColor #ffffff
  FontColor #1f2937
}
skinparam database {
  BorderColor #9fb0c7
  BackgroundColor #ffffff
}
skinparam queue {
  BorderColor #9fb0c7
  BackgroundColor #ffffff
}
skinparam folder {
  BorderColor #9fb0c7
  BackgroundColor #ffffff
}
skinparam note {
  BorderColor #d7dee8
  BackgroundColor #fbfcfe
  FontColor #445066
}

actor Browser
cloud "Google OAuth" as Google

rectangle "Edge" {
  node "Nginx\nTLS + reverse proxy" as Nginx
}

rectangle "Delivery Layer" {
  component "REST API\n/api/*" as Rest
  component "WebSocket Gateway\n/ws/*" as Ws
  component "ASGI Router\nProtocolTypeRouter" as Asgi
}

rectangle "Application Layer" {
  component "Identity & Session\nusers, profile,\nmedia access" as Identity
  component "Chat & Collaboration\nchat, messages,\nfriends, groups" as Collaboration
  component "Realtime Services\nchat consumer,\npresence, direct inbox" as Realtime
  component "Access Control & Audit\nroles, permissions,\nauditlog" as Control
}

rectangle "Infrastructure" {
  database "PostgreSQL" as Db
  queue "Redis\nchannel layer + presence" as Redis
  folder "Media Storage\navatars + attachments" as Media
  node "Observability\nPrometheus, Grafana,\nLoki, Alertmanager" as Observability
}

Rest -[hidden]down-> Ws
Ws -[hidden]down-> Asgi
Identity -[hidden]right-> Collaboration
Collaboration -[hidden]right-> Realtime
Realtime -[hidden]right-> Control
Db -[hidden]right-> Redis
Redis -[hidden]right-> Media
Media -[hidden]right-> Observability

Browser --> Nginx
Nginx --> Rest
Nginx --> Ws
Ws --> Asgi

Rest --> Identity
Rest --> Collaboration
Rest --> Control

Asgi --> Identity : ws auth
Asgi --> Realtime

Collaboration ..> Control : permission checks
Identity ..> Control : security events
Realtime ..> Control : audit + block rules

Identity --> Db
Identity --> Media
Collaboration --> Db
Collaboration --> Media
Realtime --> Redis
Realtime --> Db
Control --> Db

Google --> Identity : token validation
Observability ..> Rest : scrape health / metrics

note right of Rest
Canonical external chat entrypoint:
POST /api/chat/resolve/

Room-scoped HTTP calls use roomId.
end note

note right of Realtime
WebSocket endpoints:
- /ws/chat/<room_id>/
- /ws/presence/
- /ws/inbox/
end note

note bottom of Collaboration
Group flows include invites, join requests,
pins, moderation and ownership transfer.
end note
@enduml
